# Component Development Guidelines

## UI Components
All UI components should follow these guidelines:

### Visual Consistency
1. Colors:
   - Background: #1a1a1a (main), #2d2d2d (cards)
   - Accent: #caff17 (primary action)
   - Text: white (headers), #9ca3af (secondary)

2. Animations:
   - Use transition-all for smooth changes
   - Duration: 200ms (quick), 300ms (normal), 700ms (emphasis)
   - Include hover effects for interactive elements

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints:
  - sm: 640px
  - md: 768px
  - lg: 1024px
  - xl: 1280px

### Component Examples
1. Progress Circle [TaskProgress.jsx](mdc:task-app-frontend/src/components/TaskProgress.jsx):
   - Dynamic color based on progress
   - Smooth animations
   - Glowing effect using drop-shadows
   - Responsive sizing

2. Category Filter [CategoryFilter.jsx](mdc:task-app-frontend/src/components/CategoryFilter.jsx):
   - Horizontal scrolling on mobile
   - Arrow navigation on desktop
   - Smooth scroll behavior
   - Active state highlighting

3. Header [Header.jsx](mdc:task-app-frontend/src/components/Header.jsx):
   - Logo with hover effect
   - Gradient text
   - Responsive layout
